room_title: Escape room "Escape from Egypt" by Tri-State Escape in Huntington
room_description: A team of archaeologists have discovered the location of one of the most significant Egyptian pharaohâ€™s tomb to date, believed to be filled with gold, jewels and priceless artifacts. Whether due to the physical challenges presented getting in and out of the tomb, or the legend of the pharaoh's curse that is said to protect the burial site, no one has yet made it out alive. You and your team are determined to be the first to enter the tomb and successfully escape-- can you do it? Or will your remains become artifacts for the next team of archaeologists to uncover?
